upon probable cause , supported by oath or affirmation , and particularly describing the place to be searched , and the persons or things to be seized .	fourth_amendment
In suits at common law , where the value in controversy shall exceed twenty dollars , the right of trial by jury shall be preserved , and no fact tried by a jury , shall be otherwise reexamined in any court of the United States , than according to the rules of the common law .	seventh_amendment
The right of citizens of the United States to vote shall not be denied or abridged by the United States or by any state on account of race , color , or previous condition of servitude . The Congress shall have power to enforce this article by appropriate legislation .	amendmentxv
